            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Servilla Praepusa <lb n="2"/>filiae suae Lesbiae <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nnorum</ex></expan> XI <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ensium</ex></expan> X hic <expan><abbr>sepul</abbr><ex>tae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>evis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>erra</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>quid sibi fata velint bellissima quaeque <lb n="5"/>creari edita laeti<expan><ex>ti</ex><abbr>ae</abbr></expan> commoda si rapiu<lb break="no" n="6"/><surplus>u</surplus>nt sed quae fatorum legi serva<supplied reason="lost">r</supplied>e necesse est <lb n="7"/>perverso lacrimas fundimus officio haec bis sex <lb n="8"/>annos vix bene transierat ill&amp;lt;a=E&amp;gt; suas la<supplied reason="lost">c</supplied>rimas nondum emiserat <lb n="9"/>omnes et poterat semper flebilis esse suis parcite enim vobis tristes <lb n="10"/>sine fine parentes parcius et manes sollicitare meos ponimus hunc <lb n="11"/>titulum luctus solacia nostri qui legit ut dicat sit tibi terra levis 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Vier aneinanderpassende Fragmente. Hedera in Z. 1. Z. 1-3 in größerer Schrift. Z. 1: die letzten beiden Buchstaben in kleinerer Schrift nachträglich hinzugefügt.</p>
            </div>
